[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":271},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F":248,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F":257},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F07\u002F18\u002Fvscode-python3-venv-config\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":89,"date":232,"description":18,"extension":233,"lang":234,"meta":235,"navigation":236,"path":237,"readingMinutes":238,"seo":239,"standalone":240,"stem":241,"tags":242,"tldr":245,"updated":245,"url":246,"__hash__":247},"content\u002FPython\u002FVSCode-設置-Python3-venv-虛擬環境參數.md","VSCode 設置 Python3 venv 虛擬環境參數","814575457",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":226},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,49,56,59,74,81,84,91,94,97,100,103,126,132,138,145,150,153,159,162,171,174,180,191,199,202,208,211,222],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"最近正在寫 Python3 的時候會需要準備虛擬環境，剛好我都是用 VSCode 來開發，所以這一篇紀錄一下怎麼修改 VSCode 的 Python3 執行參數。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"虛擬環境的準備",[16,23,24],{},"首先先準備一個測試專案，打開終端機在終端機輸入以下指令：",[26,27,32],"pre",{"className":28,"code":29,"language":30,"meta":31,"style":31},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","mkdir pyTest # 建立一個 pyTest 資料夾\ncd pyTest # 移動到 pyTest 資料夾\n","cmd","",[33,34,35,43],"code",{"__ignoreMap":31},[36,37,40],"span",{"class":38,"line":39},"line",1,[36,41,42],{},"mkdir pyTest # 建立一個 pyTest 資料夾\n",[36,44,46],{"class":38,"line":45},2,[36,47,48],{},"cd pyTest # 移動到 pyTest 資料夾\n",[16,50,51,52,55],{},"然後用 VSCode 打開該資料夾，如果你有安裝 VSCode 的快速啟動包，可以直接輸入 ",[33,53,54],{},"code ."," 快速打開。",[16,57,58],{},"接下來輸入以下在 VSCode 輸入以下指令：",[26,60,62],{"className":28,"code":61,"language":30,"meta":31,"style":31},"python3 -m venv .venv # Mac\npython -m venv .venv # Window\n",[33,63,64,69],{"__ignoreMap":31},[36,65,66],{"class":38,"line":39},[36,67,68],{},"python3 -m venv .venv # Mac\n",[36,70,71],{"class":38,"line":45},[36,72,73],{},"python -m venv .venv # Window\n",[16,75,76,77,80],{},"這時候 VSCode 會生成一個 ",[33,78,79],{},".venv"," 資料夾。",[16,82,83],{},"這時候依據 VSCode 官方文件說法來講，應該是會出現以下這張圖：",[16,85,86],{},[87,88],"img",{"alt":89,"src":90},"Python","https:\u002F\u002Fcode.visualstudio.com\u002Fassets\u002Fdocs\u002Fpython\u002Fenvironments\u002Fpython-environment-prompt.png",[16,92,93],{},"(翻譯：我們發現到有一個新的虛擬環境，你要替當前工作區選擇它嗎？)",[16,95,96],{},"通常這時候按下 Yes 就可以搞定了，但是不知道為什麼我的 VSCode 毫無反應 QQ",[12,98,99],{"id":99},"解決方法",[16,101,102],{},"那麼為了解決這個問題，所以只好親自做一些設置調整，所以我們要先叫出功能選擇模式：",[104,105,106,115],"ul",{},[107,108,109,110],"li",{},"Windows\n",[104,111,112],{},[107,113,114],{},"CTRL + SHIFT + P",[107,116,117,118],{},"Mac\n",[104,119,120,123],{},[107,121,122],{},"Command + SHIFT + P",[107,124,125],{},"fn + F1 or F1",[16,127,128,129],{},"接下來在上方輸入 ",[33,130,131],{},">Python: Select Interpreter",[16,133,134],{},[87,135],{"alt":136,"src":137},"Select Interpreter","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-07-18%2013.16.10.png",[16,139,140,141,144],{},"接下來點進去後，你應該可以看到 ",[33,142,143],{},"Python 3.xx.xx 64 bit('.venv': venv)","，選它就對了",[16,146,147],{},[87,148],{"alt":79,"src":149},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-07-18%2013.17.01.png",[16,151,152],{},"設置好之後 VSCode 左下角就會顯示你當前的 Python 直譯器",[16,154,155],{},[87,156],{"alt":157,"src":158},"Interpreter","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-07-18%2013.20.05.png",[16,160,161],{},"接下來會建議將 VSCode 重新啟動一下，這樣子 VSCode 才會重新啟動一些參數，通常來講你會看到 VSCode 自動帶入這一段：",[26,163,165],{"className":28,"code":164,"language":30,"meta":31,"style":31},"source \u002FUsers\u002Frayxu\u002FpyTest\u002F.venv\u002Fbin\u002Factivate\n",[33,166,167],{"__ignoreMap":31},[36,168,169],{"class":38,"line":39},[36,170,164],{},[16,172,173],{},"代表著現在要走 .venv 的虛擬環境 Interpreter。",[16,175,176],{},[87,177],{"alt":178,"src":179},"Interpreter。","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-07-18%2013.24.15.png",[16,181,182,183,186,187,190],{},"接下來你輸入 ",[33,184,185],{},"pip list"," or ",[33,188,189],{},"pip3 list"," 應該會非常乾淨只會有以下套件：",[104,192,193,196],{},[107,194,195],{},"pip        21.1.1",[107,197,198],{},"setuptools 56.0.0",[16,200,201],{},"接下來你就可以正常的在該專案安裝套件了。",[16,203,204,205,207],{},"最後如果你發現一直無法找到 ",[33,206,143],{}," 的話，只需要關掉 VSCode 重新啟動(整個 VSCode 關掉重啟)就可以了。",[12,209,210],{"id":210},"參考文獻",[104,212,213],{},[107,214,215],{},[216,217,221],"a",{"href":218,"rel":219},"https:\u002F\u002Fstackoverflow.com\u002Fquestions\u002F54106071\u002Fhow-can-i-set-up-a-virtual-environment-for-python-in-visual-studio-code",[220],"nofollow","How can I set up a virtual environment for Python in Visual Studio Code?",[223,224,225],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":31,"searchDepth":45,"depth":45,"links":227},[228,229,230,231],{"id":14,"depth":45,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":45,"text":21},{"id":99,"depth":45,"text":99},{"id":210,"depth":45,"text":210},"2021-07-18 12:26:51","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fpython\u002Fvscode-python3-venv","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"Python\u002FVSCode-設置-Python3-venv-虛擬環境參數",[89,243,244],"venv","VSCode",null,"\u002Fpython\u002F20210718\u002F814575457\u002F","oru-sMxc-LyO5n-Xn80RvgKmOrzD8z-XzhfanP6yJXg",{"newer":249,"older":253},{"url":250,"title":251,"date":252},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20210718\u002F956160363\u002F","Java